### Implementation Guidelines
- Use the standard page patterns as templates for new pages
- Follow the root `space-y-6` container pattern consistently
- Organize content into logical white card sections
- Let MainLayout handle all page-level spacing and responsive behavior
- Maintain visual consistency across all application pages
